title: Eds FF
text:
Eds FF is a <a href="Sweden">Swedish</a> <a href="association%20Football">football</a> club located in Ed.
Background.
Eds FF currently plays in <a href="Swedish%20football%20Division%204">Division 4</a> Bohuslän/Dalsland which is the sixth tier of <a href="Swedish%20football%20league%20system">Swedish football</a>. They play their home matches at the Bergslätt IP in Ed.
The club is affiliated to <a href="Dalslands%20Fotbollf%C3%B6rbund">Dalslands Fotbollförbund</a>. Eds FF have competed in the <a href="Svenska%20Cupen">Svenska Cupen</a> on 7 occasions and have played 10 matches in the competition. They played in the <a href="2008%20Svenska%20Cupen">2008 Svenska Cupen</a> beating <a href="FC%20Trollh%C3%A4ttan">FC Trollhättan</a> by 2–1 (aet) at home in the first round before losing 1–4 at home to <a href="IF%20Brommapojkarna">IF Brommapojkarna</a> in the second round with an attendance of 600 spectators.
